	<h1 class="title">丰田想投入十亿美元研究人工智能，但要做的不是无人车</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/97532/small/97532.jpeg?1431064746" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">赵长存 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-09 12:35:49 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17285/medium/17285.jpg?1447042227" alt="" />			
	</div>
